// PHASE 2.1 SPIKE — shadcn pack's main.tsx still wires Mantine
// providers in addition to shadcn's globals.css + Sonner Toaster
// because the page templates haven't been ported to canonical
// shadcn yet (Phase 2.3).  Mantine providers stay until then so
